Shogo is the vocalist for the band 175R.

Profile

Real Name: Kinoshita Shogo

Birthday: April 24, 1980 (1980-04-24) (age 44)

Birthplace: Kitakyushu, Fukuoka, Japan

Blood Type: A

Family: Imai Eriko (ex-wife), Kinoshita Raimu (Son)
